Description.Text: This OptionSet defines flags indicating the commands a ConnectionManager may use in its call to the EstablishConnections Method.

The Role is allowed to establish, close, and modify connections between FunctionalEntities. This includes reading and writing connection configuration settings, reading endpoint and connection capabilities, and executing methods related to management of connections. It is intended to be a non-human Role.
